Ripe,Development,is,a,company,that,provides,consulting,services,and,web,based,applications,Two,such,applications,are,provided,freely,on,their,website,The,Local,Time,API,returns,the,local,time,for,a,given,zip,code,The,Zip,Code,Information,API,retrieves,information,for,a,given,zip,code,that,includes,area,codes,time,zone,city,and,state,Both,services,can,be,accessed,directly,through,the,website,or,programmatically,using,XML,formatted,SOAP,calls